{"tid":866651,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"做番私影妹 江嘉敏孤男寡女山邊公然剝裙","createTime":"2018-10-18T04:41:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T06:09:00.000Z","uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"77014da1945b22cc3be65920454580407a0e94b0","tid":866651,"uid":157545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181018/photo/bkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_02b.jpg?20181018103644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20181018103644&h=2b44cf03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年23歲、有「宅男咪神」之稱的江嘉敏（Kaman）早於17歲以模特兒身份入娛樂圈，期間曾做「私影妹」，拍下不少火辣水着照。去年憑劇集中的「學生Look」成功上位的她，因形象清純被視為新一代「宅男咪神」，備受無綫力捧，可惜其後緋聞多多，被網民封為「進擊發電機」。她早前更被本報踢爆搭上身高六呎、年約30歲的電競公司高層Anthony，還於西貢築「私竇」方便蜜會，事後她亦大方承認戀情。<br />\n<br />\n表情多多大解放<br />\n<br />\n日前Kaman做回老本行擔任「私影妹」，當日她出席活動後，即由一名男友人驅車接載返回西貢「私竇」，但下車後卻未有返回寓所，反而雙雙步往附近一個較為僻靜的山頭。見兩人於山邊徘徊一會，似在揀選拍攝地點，及後她就吩咐男友人充當攝影師。當日穿白色長袖外套襯青綠色長裙的Kaman，甫埋位已經模特兒上身，自動波擺出不同甫士，動作表情多多，不時朱唇半張，再加上一對「高潮眼」，極盡挑逗，難怪她愈影愈㷫，要大解放「變身」！<br />\n<br />\n左攝右攝為晒線<br />\n<br />\nKaman指手畫腳與攝影師講了幾句後，便從袋中取出一條螢光粉紅色短褲，更當着男友人面前，穿上短褲後極速脫下長裙，作風豪放，即使有居民於附近經過，她亦當對方透明，任𥄫唔嬲。穿上Bra Top的她更剝上癮，將外套的拉鏈愈拉愈低，大騷事業線，又將外套左攝右攝露出小蠻腰，足足企在山邊影了半個多小時後才捨得回家。但數分鐘後，又見Kaman換上粉紅色衞衣再出來會合男友人，轉往另一場景繼續影，最終又影了十數分鐘才收手，與男友人道別後返回寓所。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181018/photo/bkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_04b.jpg?20181018103644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_04b.jpg%3F20181018103644&h=9b799d53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181018/photo/bkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_05b.jpg?20181018103644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_05b.jpg%3F20181018103644&h=1a5cf874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181018/photo/bkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_06b.jpg?20181018103644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F20181018103644&h=4242515c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181018/photo/bkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_07b.jpg?20181018103644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_07b.jpg%3F20181018103644&h=c367347b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181018/photo/bkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_08b.jpg?20181018103644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181018%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181018000157914-1018_00862_001_08b.jpg%3F20181018103644&h=20723fb2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be3b3c55d3b639edd0ec4e3d1a5fa31e77617a00","tid":866651,"uid":216709,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:43:26.000Z","msg":"東網<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己比錢買曝光率"},{"pid":"ed0073c2ae4537da37a2ab167617b6b6a4a8aaac","tid":866651,"uid":187131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:43:31.000Z","msg":"咪又係"},{"pid":"138a934a5c4939063851970a9e883bbde067db03","tid":866651,"uid":36316,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 褲都除埋你俾啲咁嘅野我睇？"},{"pid":"d0912741f3f05fff750d75edfc6b0522065aeabc","tid":866651,"uid":3194,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"狗屎垃圾都叫得女神<img src=\"/ass